<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>- وَيُسَنُّ فِي غَيْرِهِ.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَشُرِطَ فِي شَاهِدٍ:</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[١]</span> إِسْلَامٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[٢]</span> وَبُلُوغٌ.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[٣]</span> وَعَقْلٌ.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[٤]</span> وَنُطْقٌ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>- لَكِنْ تُقْبَلُ مِنْ أَخْرَسَ بِخَطِّهِ، وَمِمَّنْ يُفِيقُ حَالَ إِفَاقَتِهِ.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[٥]</span> وَعَدَالَةٌ،<span class="c5"> وَيُعْتَبَرُ لَهَا شَيْئَانِ:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>١) الأَوَّلُ مِنْهُمَا <span class="c2">(١)</span>: الصَّلَاحُ فِي الدِّينِ،<span class="c5"> وَهُوَ:</span><a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>- أَدَاءُ الفَرَائِضِ بِرَوَاتِبِهَا.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>- وَاجْتِنَابُ المَحَارِمِ؛ بِأَلَّا يَأْتِيَ كَبِيرَةً، وَلَا يُدْمِنَ عَلَى صَغِيرَةٍ.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">٢) الثَّانِي:</span> اسْتِعْمَالُ المُرُوءَةِ بِفِعْلِ مَا يُزَيِّنُهُ وَيُجَمِّلُهُ، وَتَرْكِ مَا يُدَنِّسُهُ وَيَشِينُهُ.<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>-<span class="c5"> وَلَا تُقْبَلُ:</span><a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>- شَهَادَةُ بَعْضِ عَمُودَيِ النَّسَبِ <span class="c2">(٢)</span> لِبَعْضٍ.<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<hr>
<p class="hamesh">(١) قوله: (منهما) سقطت من (أ) و (د).<br>(٢) في (أ): نسبه.</p> </div>